  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "Spread a thin layer of vegan cheese spread on one slice of baguette bread.",
    "Add pickled vegetables evenly over the cheese.",
    "Drizzle lemon juice over the top and sprinkle with salt.",
    "Place the other slice of baguette on top to create an open sandwich. Press lightly to adhere.",
    "Bake for 10-12 minutes or until golden brown and crispy around the edges.",
    "Let cool slightly before serving."
